         <abstract>
            <p>For 2 ≤ s ≤ 12 we determine good parameters in a general construction of node sets for s-dimensional quasi-Monte Carlo integration recently introduced by the third author. Some of the parameters represent optimal choices in this construction and lead to improvements on node sets obtained by earlier techniques.</p>
          </abstract>
